Question: Are the glasses to the left or to the right of the person the woman is sitting next to?

Reference Answer: right

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n49310.jpg

Original program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='person')
IMAGE0=CROP_RIGHTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='glasses')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX1)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'right' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'left'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
